  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Restaurant Le Terrace</strong> faces the sea and offers a large buffet breakfast and four courses for dinner (summer only). You'll eat here if you're on half board. Dinner can be swapped for lunch.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Diana</strong> is exclusively for guests of the hotel. Enjoy Mediterranean cuisine that’s influenced by the flavours of Liguria.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant La Rotonda sul Mare</strong> is the hotel’s gourmet restaurant, serving refined cuisine using fresh seafood.</p>
<p><strong>The Poolside Snackbar</strong> is a great choice for a casual lunch under the shade of the olive trees. Normally open mid June to August.</p>
<p><strong>The Lounge Bar</strong> welcomes guests for a pre-dinner drink or aperitif. Choose from local wines, cocktails and over 70 kinds of Scottish whisky.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
