  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>The Grand Hotel Diana Majestic has two pools to choose from; one with lanes where you can swim against the current and another heated pool that’s designed for relaxation. The pools are usually open from May to mid October (subject to weather conditions). The pool bar is open from mid June to the end of August. </p>
<p>There’s also the private beach (open from around June to mid October) where you’ll be allocated two sun loungers and a parasol per room. It's possible to upgrade to the first or second rows for a supplement. Beach towels can be provided for approx. €3.50 per day.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free bicycle hire (subject to availability)</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking (subject to availability)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
