  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Diana Majestic is a great base to explore <a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Liguria</a> and even the French Riviera. The town's station has regular trains that stop all along the coastline and have amazing sea views. Get closer to the sea at the hotel's private beach - the water's clear and the beach is sandy. There's also two pools and lovely gardens to relax in. Take the short walk into town in the evening for a pre-dinner drink or nightcap.</p>]]></listingDescription>
