  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are finished in a modern style and have balconies with park or partial sea views. Facilities include air conditioning, TV, minibar, WiFi, safe, slippers and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Executive Rooms</strong> have a warm, welcoming atmosphere. The balconies face the pool and have a side sea view. These rooms have a shower. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> have an elegant style with a balcony and views over the gulf of Dianese and the hotel’s pools.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are about 23<span>m² and </span>enjoy a prime position at the front of the hotel with a balcony and sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are about 40<span>m², some have terraces and sea views. These rooms are</span> available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Single Occupancy Classic Rooms</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
